            "turnID": "T02",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:17:00",
            "utterance": "와 진짜구경온학생은 50명정도인건가?"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U03",
            "turnID": "T03",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:17:00",
            "utterance": "50명도안될걸?"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U04",
            "turnID": "T04",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:18:00",
            "utterance": "처...참..."
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U05",
            "turnID": "T04",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:18:00",
            "utterance": "#@이름#"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U06",
            "turnID": "T05",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:18:00",
            "utterance": "그중에서 또 몇명은 다른 학과에서보낸학생이거든"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U07",
            "turnID": "T05",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:18:00",
            "utterance": "#@이모티콘#"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U08",
            "turnID": "T06",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:18:00",
            "utterance": "ㅋㅋㅂㄱㅋㅋ진짜구경간애30명은되겠니..."
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U09",
            "turnID": "T07",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:20:00",
            "utterance": "뭔가씁쓸해ㅋㅋ처음정치시작할땐 뭐 기대된다 어쩐다 엄청핫이슈였는데"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U10",
            "turnID": "T08",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:20:00",
            "utterance": "그러게...사람이어쩌다이렇게추락했는지"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U11",
            "turnID": "T08",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:21:00",
            "utterance": "근데 그 프랑스남자는왜라인이좋대?"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U12",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:25:00",
            "utterance": "카톡이 더 귀엽긴한데"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U13",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:25:00",
            "utterance": "한국와서알았고"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U14",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:25:00",
            "utterance": "라인은 프랑스있을때부터써서"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U15",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:25:00",
            "utterance": "친숙해서좋대"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U16",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:25:00",
            "utterance": "유럽엔 이런 귀여운캐릭터가없다면서"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U17",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:26:00",
            "utterance": "그리고 있어도 일본캐릭터인데"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U18",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:26:00",
            "utterance": "그건 너무여성스러워서 별로래"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U19",
            "turnID": "T09",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "16:26:00",
            "utterance": "라인이나 카톡은 중성적이래ㅋㅋ"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U20",
            "turnID": "T10",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2018-04-13",
            "time": "17:31:00",
            "utterance": "오 글쿠나....ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ진짜신기하다"
